name: Death Mask
description: Sylvia never skimped on self care. She was meticulous about her routines, and even though self-care looked different at different phases of her life, she never took it for granted. She once asked her followers “Why don’t we do self-care every day? We can take the time to put ourselves in a positive energy that will help us make the most of the day. We can even do it in a hurry.” We’re selling Sylvia’s finest coconut and aloe face mask.
